title: Deposit for Listing Campaign
body:
MXC Exchange is running a campaign for listing Creed. 300+ Creed holders are required to deposit Creed to the exchange before Sep 7 - 19:30 (UTC+8). 
This is a proposal to make use of the governance page to track the number of Creed holders participating in the listing campaign. Click YES if you've made a deposit.
author: 0xD4415721652e871803DB7A8B7477299DBBB58D73
